<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(فقال)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: <span class="c2">(أفلا)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> قالوا: نحن <span class="c2">(في)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> الجنة <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
